{"tid":2306311,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華府擬把中芯國際和中海油納入限制投資黑名單","createTime":"2020-11-30T10:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T12:36:23.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e90b6f3da67a72dc62919244fc30e416f41a2b52","tid":2306311,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"華府擬把中芯國際和中海油納入限制投資黑名單<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562764-20201130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562764-20201130.htm&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=98856838\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1562764-20201130.htm&h=00b54dc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1562764-20201130.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n《路透社》引述消息指，美國總統特朗普政府準備將中芯國際和中海油，納入與中國解放軍關係密切的黑名單。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前簽署行政命令，禁止美國企業或個人，投資被指與中國軍方關係密切的31間中國公司。早前已經有報道指，國防部計劃追加多4間中國企業入黑名單，令總數增至35間。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》引述文件和3個消息來源說，另外兩間中企是中國建設科技集團，以及中國國際工程諮詢公司。<br />\n<br />\n中芯國際否認與中國軍方有關，表示產品和服務只作民用和商業用途，不為軍方製造產品，公司繼續與美國政府進行建設性和公開的接觸。<br />\n<br />\n美國國防部、中國駐美大使館和中海油暫時未有回應。"},{"pid":"8043cec5212edd167bfe8d2451e25329c538bb43","tid":2306311,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}